ShiftedSafeguard Discord Bot Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 29/08/2023

This Privacy Policy explains how ShiftedSafeguard ("we," "us," "our") collects, uses, and protects any personal information or data that you provide or that is generated while using the ShiftedSafeguard Discord bot ("the bot").

1. Information Collection

We do not collect any personal information from users of the bot. The bot operates within the Discord platform and does not have the capability to access, store, or retrieve personal data.

2. Usage Data

The bot may collect and store usage data, including commands issued, messages sent, and other interactions within the server. This data is used solely for the purpose of improving the bot's functionality and performance.

3. Data Storage

All data collected by the bot is stored within the Discord platform and is subject to Discord's privacy policies and terms of service. We do not have access to or control over the data stored by Discord.

4. Cookies and Tracking

The bot does not use cookies or tracking technologies to gather information from users.

5. Third-party Services

The bot may interact with third-party services and APIs to provide certain features. Users are encouraged to review the privacy policies of these third-party services for more information on their data practices.

6. Security

We are committed to ensuring the security of the data collected by the bot. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure. While we strive to protect your data, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

7. Changes to Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. It is advised to review this policy periodically.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the data collected by the bot, please contact us on [Discord](https://discord.gg/ww2BePEXmD).
